Anglo American’s Los Bronces Mine Returned to Normal Operations

-- B y   S e b a s t i a n   B o y d   a n d   M a t t   C r a z e
-- 
2011-09-25T13:08:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/anglo-american-s-los-bronces-mine-returned-to-normal-operations.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL) ’s Los Bronces
copper mine returned to normal operations at 1 a.m. New York
time after a power outage that blacked out the country’s central
regions yesterday, Anglo American spokesman Marcelo Esquivel
wrote in an e-mail.  A crusher at the mine had been working partially during the
outage.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sebastian Boyd in Santiago at 
 sboyd9@bloomberg.net ;
Matthew Craze in Santiago at 
 mcraze@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net . 